item.title: How do i change it back?
item.dc:creator: @primadude Primadude
item.description:
@primadude wrote:

Open up the start menu > Right click ‘My computer’ > Click properties > Click the advanced tab > Click environmental variables.

jc22493:

Start > My Computer > Right click > Properties > Advanced > Environmental Variables > Woot!

Ah got there before me :(.
